                            <comment id="13560140" author="daijy" created="Tue, 22 Jan 2013 22:54:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are multiple root causes:&lt;br/&gt;
1. There is no distinguish between backend and frontend in illustrate&lt;br/&gt;
2. ReadToEndLoader (invoked by POLoader, only used in illustrate) does not invoke setLocation&lt;br/&gt;
3. ReadToEndLoader does not have signature&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is also a fix in HCat side tracked by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HCATALOG-163&quot; title=&quot;NPE when illustrating a relation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HCATALOG-163&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HCATALOG-163&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
